{"tid":150764,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球壇恥辱：疤狗。","createTime":"2017-03-10T10:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T11:48:35.000Z","uid":51171,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2bf4ad323c31ccfa3be110c419d636e2802a6de","tid":150764,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T10:01:52.000Z","msg":"贏親都係靠啲大爭議嘅入球，冇球證幫呢隊賤狗垃圾攞撚到咁多盃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我皇就唔撚靠球證，冇一場唔係靠自己乾乾淨淨贏返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />輸過俾我皇嘅全部都表示心服口服<br />\n<br />\n垃圾疤屌我皇嗰陣唔好諗住拋低一句：你咪又係黑，就走左去，俾啲例子黎聽下，我都想知究竟我皇有邊場係黑返黎(俾到嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n皇馬：球壇典範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9752f0ef353bc8c3c70aa23c7bb2fae0b35d68","tid":150764,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"曲到圓"},{"pid":"acd4ff28f901cbca23bbc86f753d28ec00d5918b","tid":150764,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"我皇乃波台公認典範<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f43763c4aef46856aba601534a5ce91c0bdfa1d","tid":150764,"uid":68199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"直線抽擊"},{"pid":"62407aefeb1d7fb4a9bcf91fd3ad7a0a37c5e5f7","tid":150764,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:11:11.000Z","msg":"十隻疤狗仔負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8048db98e179c5134cccfaadcbca0b1065feea52","tid":150764,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:44:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十隻疤狗仔負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq